description: Woodstock foodies are flocking by the dozens to JZ’s for every incredible pizza that comes out of their mobile brick oven. Born from a desire to feed sporting event goers something a bit more exciting than homemade sandwiches from a cooler, this big black truck is now not only bringing a wonderful selection of pizza perfection to the sporty scene, but also catering to all sorts of fun festivities; weddings, birthdays, corporate events, etc… and everyone who tries a bite of JZ’s delightful pizza with the perfect wood-fired taste and toppings of the highest quality, declares that they have a new favorite pizza ever, then immediately commences their cravings for the next fix. For tasty pizza that’s an absolute treat, call on JZ's to cater your next feast.
name: JZ's Brick Oven Pizza
